# DEPRECATED — kept only as a record of required env var names.
# Secrets are now managed via 1Password (see .env.tpl).
#
# Local development:
#   1. Install 1Password CLI: brew install --cask 1password-cli
#   2. Enable "Integrate with 1Password CLI" in 1Password app → Settings → Developer
#   3. `npm run dev` (wraps vite with `op run --env-file=.env.tpl`)
#
# Cloudflare Pages production:
#   Env vars are configured in the Cloudflare dashboard, not via this template.

# Required env var names (values resolved via 1Password):
# YOUTUBE_API_KEY  — YouTube Data API v3 (Prod-Apps vault)
